│ (!isUsedOutsideOfLoop(Ind->getInduction(), L))\n    continue;\n\n  //                      │
│ ...\n}\n```\n\n**Proposed Change**:\n\n```cpp\n// Edit at line 9758\nfor (auto *Ind :      │
